lead_paragraph: Jalen Jones scored 17 of his 20 points in the second half to lead No. 10 Texas A&M to a 66-53 victory over Missouri on Saturday, extending the Aggies' winning streak to 10 games.

headline.print_headline: Jones Scores 20 as No. 10 A&M Gets 66-53 Win Over Missouri
